@startuml
title ЭТАП 2: Параллельная классификация (Ансамбль ИИ)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam noteTextAlignment left

participant "MainParser" as Main
participant "Stage2ClassificationManager" as Manager
participant "Stage2MistralClient" as Client
participant "Mistral AI API" as API

Main -> Manager : classify(candidate)\nline:73\n(CodeCandidate object)
activate Manager

loop Для каждой из 7 голов (H1..H7)
    Manager -> Client : sendRequest(context, role, headName)\nline:26\n(String context, String role, String head)
    activate Client

    Client -> Client : buildSystemPrompt(role + description)\nline:28\n(Internal logic)

    Client -> API : HTTP POST /chat/completions\nline:47\n(JSON: model, messages, format, temp)
    note right: Код: "db.execute(sql)"\nИнструкция: "Верни JSON"

    API --> Client : HTTP 200 Response\n(JSON: choices[0].message.content)

    Client -> Client : parseResponse(body)\nline:68\n(Returns LLMVerdict)

    Client --> Manager : (LLMVerdict object: class, confidence, head)\n(Return result)
    deactivate Client
end

Manager -> Manager : CompletableFuture.join()\nline:33\n(Synchronize 7 threads)

Manager --> Main : (List<LLMVerdict>)\n(Return all verdicts)
deactivate Manager

note over Main, DB : Далее данные передаются в MistralArbitrator\nдля взвешенного голосования
@enduml